01:25:07,703 --> 01:25:11,310
what this nobody, this non
entity has in his heart.

1280
01:25:25,887 --> 01:25:28,889
I looked for you at the bar.

1281
01:25:28,890 --> 01:25:30,961
Any luck on the job from?

1282
01:25:33,095 --> 01:25:34,095
Nothing.

1283
01:25:35,564 --> 01:25:38,067
Lieutenant Milliet
says I should enlist.

1284
01:25:38,068 --> 01:25:39,467
What for?

1285
01:25:39,468 --> 01:25:42,574
Well I'm good at
fighting, aren't I?

1286
01:25:45,440 --> 01:25:48,609
Roulin's have always been that.

1287
01:25:48,610 --> 01:25:52,353
The trick is to know
what you're fighting for.

1288
01:25:55,117 --> 01:25:57,084
Would you look at it?

1289
01:25:57,085 --> 01:26:00,032
There's a whole
other world up there.

1290
01:26:01,590 --> 01:26:05,367
Something we get to gaze upon
but don't fully understand.

1291
01:26:07,262 --> 01:26:08,832
It reminds me of him.

1292
01:26:12,100 --> 01:26:15,343
It feels wrong all
that life snuffed out

1293
01:26:16,338 --> 01:26:18,682
because of a stupid accident.

1294
01:26:20,475 --> 01:26:25,312
I'm still wondering why he
would cover for those boys.

1295
01:26:25,313 --> 01:26:26,986
What I'm wondering is if people

1296
01:26:26,987 --> 01:26:29,223
will appreciate what he did.

1297
01:26:36,491 --> 01:26:38,402
You were looking for me?

1298
01:26:40,328 --> 01:26:44,065
This arrived from
Holland this morning.

1299
01:26:44,066 --> 01:26:46,239
It's from Jo, Theo's widow.

1300
01:26:47,836 --> 01:26:51,045
It turns out Gachel
did send the letter.

1301
01:26:54,309 --> 01:26:58,052
And, she was terribly
touched by what you did.

1302
01:26:59,514 --> 01:27:01,015
She thought it only right
that you should know

1303
01:27:01,016 --> 01:27:05,152
what was in it, so she
copied it out for us.

1304
01:27:05,153 --> 01:27:08,322
She sends her, she
said something about-

1305
01:27:08,323 --> 01:27:10,234
- Alright, give it here.

1306
01:27:16,364 --> 01:27:19,038
In the life of the painter,

1307
01:27:19,039 --> 01:27:22,903
death may perhaps not be
the most difficult thing.

1308
01:27:22,904 --> 01:27:27,775
For myself, I declare I
don't Know anything about it.

1309
01:27:27,776 --> 01:27:32,513
But, the sight of the stars
always makes me dream.

1310
01:27:32,514 --> 01:27:35,552
Why I say to myself should
those spots of light

1311
01:27:35,553 --> 01:27:38,919
in the firmament bet
Inaccessible lo us?

1312
01:27:38,920 --> 01:27:42,094
Maybe we can take
death to go to a star

1313
01:27:43,592 --> 01:27:46,227
and lo die peacefully of
old age would be to go there

1314
01:27:46,228 --> 01:27:47,228
on foot.

1315
01:27:49,765 --> 01:27:51,938
For the moment, I'm
going to go to bed

1316
01:27:51,939 --> 01:27:56,937
because it's late, and I wish
you goodnight and good luck

1317
01:27:56,938 --> 01:28:00,044
with a handshake,
your loving Vincent.

